://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 65 Olympians competed in 16 sports in Paris and 59 of them brought home gold medals and they are on a three-day visit in Hong Kong before leaving for Macao Special Administrative Region on Saturday.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993544556484, \"rank\": 6.455447467176901e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9972042731886501, \"rank\": 0.002792915377344734, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"score\": 0.9999999973736067, \"rank\": 2.625401635160486e-09, \"text\": \"Macao\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macau\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.8865579140054654, \"rank\": 0.12795789667025662, \"text\": \"Special Administrative Region\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is my first time to visit Hong Kong as a member of the Chinese mainland delegation,\\\" the men's singles table tennis champion Fan Zhendong told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9972042731886501, \"rank\": 0.002792915377344734, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\"