ng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am quite familiar with Hong Kong,\\\" said Zhang Yufei who earned one silver and five bronze swimming medals at the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9972042731886501, \"rank\": 0.002792915377344734, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9727864122994488, \"rank\": 0.027972027972030022, \"text\": \"Zhang Yufei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I came to compete, I often went to eat local cuisines like har gow (crystal shrimp dumplings) and cha siu bao.\\\"\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an honor for me to visit Hong Kong for the fourth time as a member of the Chinese mainland delegation,\\\" Chinese table tennis team captain Ma Long told reporters.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9972042731886501, \"rank\": 0.002792915377344734, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9993955479753804, \"rank\": 0.0006048176079068852, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1362, \"end